My teacher&#39;s name is $myTeacher. $teacherPronoun gives us homework to do. The first thing I always do is write my name, $myName, on it, so that my teacher knows that it&#39;s mine. 
[[Needing Help]]


:: Needing Help [ story]{"position":"412,340","size":"100,100"}
Sometimes, the homework is too hard, so I have to ask my friend $myFriend to help me. $friendPronouns always helps me, which is why I remember to always say please when I&#39;m asking her for help, and thank you after she has helped me. 
[[Helping Others]]

:: Helping Others [ story]{"position":"413,489","size":"100,100"}
Other times, I understand the homework very well, and my friends ask me for help. I try my best to help them, especially when they say please. 
After I help them, I feel very happy, especially if they say thank you.

